title: Start
body:
You walk up to the President and EP.
"Heyyy!" EP smiles at you.
"What's up!" EP smiles at you too.

[[It's good!|201]]
[[Great!|201]]

"Oh my god aren't you like so excited for the party tonight?" EP jumps and down a little bit.

[[I can't wait!!|301]]
[[It's going to be amazingggg.|301]]

"I know, right?" she smiles even wider. "I can't wait either!"
"We were just talking about what mixers to bring and everything," President says. "Oh, by the way, what mixers do you think we should buy? I was just telling Ellie what to buy."

[[Coke.|401]]
[[Um, more alcohol, haha.|402]]

"Hahaha, don't worry, we've got plenty," President laughs. "We're gonna need something else, though."
"Oh, you should get lemonade! Lemonade is so good with vodka," EP lights up.
"Lemonade is way too sugary, EP," President laughs. "I don't want my teeth to get yellow."
"oh yea, you're totally right, I guess I didn't think about that," EP says. "You're right, lemonade is disgusting."
"Well, I think I'll tell her to grab orange juice. There's a lot of low-sugar orange juice," President nods. "I'll be right back."
She turns around and leaves the conversation.

[[So, how's it going?|501]]
[[What's up?|501]]

"Hmmm... I don't know," President ponders for a moment.
"Oh, you should get lemonade! Lemonade is so good with vodka," EP lights up.
"Lemonade is way too sugary, EP," President laughs. "I don't want my teeth to get yellow."
"oh yea, you're totally right, I guess I didn't think about that," EP says. "You're right, lemonade is disgusting."
"Well, I think I'll tell her to grab orange juice. There's a lot of low-sugar orange juice," President nods. "I'll be right back."
She turns around and leaves the conversation.

[[So, how's it going?|501]]
[[What's up?|501]]

"It's great!!" EP giggles forcefully. "I still can't believe we're here! It's so amazing."

[[Yea, it's great!|601]]
[[I know, it's like, pretty overwhelming, haha.|602]]

"I know, it's like, crazy," she nods. "But everyone is so nice and welcoming, I'm like, so comfortable around them, haha. I've spent all morning thinking about how great the party's going to be and what it's going to be like. What do you think is going to happen?"

[[Um everyone's probably going to get really drunk.|702]]
[[It's going to be crazy!!|702]]

"I've been spending all day wondering what the party's going to be like!" EP puts her hands together. "I bet it's going to be so crazy, haha. What do you think?"

[[Um, everyone's probably going to get really drunk.|702]]
[[It's going to be crazy!!|702]]

"Oh my god, yea, I know. I wonder who's going to smash the pinata," she wonders.

[[What?|801]]
[[The pinata?|801]]

Her brow furrows. "Well, yea, the pinata! Every party has to have a pinata, that's like, the one thing about parties I know for sure, haha." She's serious.

[[I haven't been to a party with a pinata in years.|901]]
[[Aren't those, like, a kid's thing?|902]]

"Oh, well yea, it was a joke, haha," she touches your shoulder. "It's like going to be so crazy though!"

[[Yes!!|1001]]
[[I know right.|1001]]

"Oh, well yea, it was like, a joke, haha," she touches your shoulder. "It's like going to be so crazy though!"

[[Yes!!|1001]]
[[I know right.|1001]]

"Yes!!" She smiles.

[[I think I have to go get ready, haha.|1101]]
[[I have to go but I'll see you later!|1101]]
